          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官三位，可是饮酒的么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王殿臣、郭起凤",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请到楼上坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带路。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同上楼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "取酒来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "暖酒一壶吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放在案上，唤你再来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "举杯痛饮消愁恨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "思想狂徒怒在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抢夺妇女天怎容！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸、计全同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是酒楼，待我沽饮几杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒保！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位是喝酒的么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请到楼上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带路。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸、计全、酒保同上楼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！上面乃是大……"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……大……大家吃酒，大家打钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说客人，这一张桌子，你老可是不能坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何坐不得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这张桌子，乃是谢九太爷的座位。他不定是什么时候来，如若来时，我们可是"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃罪不起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们暂且坐了，等他到来，再让与他便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，我在外面招呼着；他一来，你们二位，可就起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休得多言，拿酒来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计们，拿暖酒一壶吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唤你再来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恨强徒行事太胆大，"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "欺压良民罪可杀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！可恼吓，可恼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭起凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可惨吓，可惨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王殿臣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可恶吓，可恶！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！可恨吓，可恨！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保急上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人快快请开，九太爷一会就来！你快请到那边去坐，我好把桌子收拾干净。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有俺在此，料无妨碍。等他到来，俺与他答话。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个事儿不妥当，只怕要闹糟糕。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位请酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王殿臣、郭起凤",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他言道强徒就来到，"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "等他来时观看分晓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可了不得了，谢九太爷已经来到啦！客官，快躲一躲吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "谢虎",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急急风〗。谢虎上，上楼，看，翻桌。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！俺正在此饮酒，你将桌儿打翻，是何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "谢虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了！尔莫非瞎了尔的狗眼！你九太爷在此，是谁人不知，谁人不晓？俺这靴"
        },
        {
          "character": "谢虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尖一动，管叫你死无有葬身之地！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你口出狂言，莫非吃了熊心豹胆！"
        },
        {
          "character": "谢虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前有一松林，你可敢去，与俺较量么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢说松林，就是虎穴龙潭，你老爷何惧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "谢虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸、谢虎同下，计全追下，施世纶、王殿臣、郭起凤同下。）"
        }
      ],
