    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "秃子",
        "谢虎",
        "黄天霸"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四头目、秃子同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秃子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众好汉，你我同到郊外！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四头目、秃子同转场，同下。黄天霸、谢虎同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此松林，你我怎样比试？"
        },
        {
          "character": "谢虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你九太爷自出世以来，从不杀这无名之辈。尔且通上名来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且听了：你老爷家住江南绍兴府金华县，飞镖黄三泰之子、四霸天赛罗成黄"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天霸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "谢虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天霸，你既生在绿林，就该以义气当先，为何苦害天下英雄，每每与绿林作对？"
        },
        {
          "character": "谢虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日遇见你九太爷，只怕你难逃性命！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀呀呸！想你这厮在此，不安本分，霸占民女，欺压良民，就该随俺到施大人"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "台前认罪，尔还敢出此狂言！今日相逢，可谓冤家对头了。休走，看刀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "谢虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢。你我今日比武，不许用暗器伤人。如用暗器伤人，算不得英雄后代。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丈夫一言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "谢虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂能反悔。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸、谢虎同起打，对单刀。谢虎下，黄天霸追下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "秃子→黄天霸",
