        "贺仁杰"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四头目、秃子同上，施世纶、郭起凤同上。秃子看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秃子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看那人好似那赃官的模样，我等赶上前去，将他掳掠便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秃子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四头目、秃子抢施世纶同下。贺仁杰、王殿臣同上，四头目、秃子、施世纶同上，贺仁杰截打，四头目、"
        },
        {
          "character": "秃子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秃子同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天霸与谢虎，在松林比武，你快去帮助便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺仁杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贺仁杰下。施世纶、王殿臣、郭起凤同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
