    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "谢虎"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（谢虎上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "谢虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。看天霸杀法厉害，毒药镖伤他便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸追上，开打，谢虎败，上桌。黄天霸追上，谢虎持镖打，黄天霸倒地。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "谢虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天霸吓，天霸！你往日英名，哪里去了！待俺将他的首级割下。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（谢虎下桌，砍。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "谢虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看刀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贺仁杰上，踢刀落地。贺仁杰、谢虎同起打。谢虎败下，贺仁杰背黄天霸下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
