    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "施世纶",
        "朱光祖",
        "李堃",
        "王殿臣",
        "贺仁杰",
        "郭起凤"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、王殿臣、郭起凤、朱光祖、金大力、李堃、施世纶同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心中恨谢虎，定要把贼除。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王殿臣、郭起凤、朱光祖、金大力、李堃",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人受惊了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄天霸可曾回衙？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王殿臣、郭起凤、朱光祖、金大力、李堃",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "并未回衙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他与那谢虎比武，本院也曾命贺仁杰前去帮助，怎么这时候，还不见回来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王殿臣、郭起凤、朱光祖、金大力、李堃",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想必来也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贺仁杰背黄天霸上，扶黄天霸卧椅。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺仁杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叩见大人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。这天霸是怎么样了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺仁杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄叔父被谢虎暗用金镖，将他打倒，故而如此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他为何昏迷不醒？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀大人：那谢虎惯用金镖伤人，但是他的镖，俱用毒药冶过，打在身上，有"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个时辰，药性发作，只用七天，这性命可就不保了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此便怎么样救他性命才好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李堃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朱爷与谢虎，乃是一师之徒，难道说这毒药镖就无有解救之法么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺仁杰、王殿臣、郭起凤、金大力",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解救之法倒有，必得我师父红旗李玉，在集贤村居住。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此先将天霸抬至后面调养，就命朱光祖速到集贤村讨药便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉了大人命，讨药拜师尊。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位请至后面，好好看守天霸，等候灵药便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
